msgstr "<command>kdiff3</command> --help"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example output:"
msgstr "Näidisväljund:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:281
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Options:\n"
#| "  -m, --merge               Merge the input.\n"
#| "  -b, --base file           Explicit base file. For compatibility with "
#| "certain tools.\n"
#| "  -o, --output file         Output file. Implies -m. E.g.: -o newfile."
#| "txt\n"
#| "  --out file                Output file, again. (For compatibility with "
#| "certain tools.)\n"
#| "  --auto                    No GUI if all conflicts are auto-solvable. "
#| "(Needs -o file)\n"
#| "  --qall                    Don't solve conflicts automatically. (For "
#| "compatibility...)\n"
#| "  --L1 alias1               Visible name replacement for input file 1 "
#| "(base).\n"
#| "  --L2 alias2               Visible name replacement for input file 2.\n"
#| "  --L3 alias3               Visible name replacement for input file 3.\n"
#| "  -L, --fname alias         Alternative visible name replacement. Supply "
#| "this once for every input.\n"
#| "  --cs string               Override a config setting. Use once for every "
#| "setting. E.g.: --cs \"AutoAdvance=1\"\n"
#| "  --confighelp              Show list of config settings and current "
#| "values.\n"
#| "  --config file             Use a different config file."
msgid ""
"Options:\n"
"  -m, --merge               Merge the input.\n"
"  -b, --base file           Explicit base file. For compatibility with "
"certain tools.\n"
"  -o, --output file         Output file. Implies -m. E.g.: -o newfile.txt\n"
"  --out file                Output file, again. (For compatibility with "
"certain tools.)\n"
"  --noauto                  Ignore --auto and always show GUI.\n"
"  --auto                    No GUI if all conflicts are auto-solvable. "
"(Needs -o file)\n"
"  --L1 alias1               Visible name replacement for input file 1 "
"(base).\n"
"  --L2 alias2               Visible name replacement for input file 2.\n"
"  --L3 alias3               Visible name replacement for input file 3.\n"
"  -L, --fname alias         Alternative visible name replacement. Supply "
"this once for every input.\n"
"  --cs string               Override a config setting. Use once for every "
"setting. E.g.: --cs \"AutoAdvance=1\"\n"
"  --confighelp              Show list of config settings and current "
"values.\n"
"  --config file             Use a different config file."
msgstr ""
"Võtmed:\n"
"  -m, --merge               Sisendi liitmine.\n"
"  -b, --base fail           Baasfail. Ühilduvuseks teatud tööriistadega.\n"
"  -o, --output fail         Väljundfail. Eelduseks -m. Nt.: -o newfile.txt\n"
"  --out fail                Taas väljundfail. (Ühilduvuseks teatud "
"tööriistadega.)\n"
"  --auto                    GUI puudub, kui kõik konfliktid on automaatselt "
"lahenevad. (Vajalik on -o file)\n"
"  --qall                    Konflikte ei lahendata automaatselt. "
"(Ühilduvuseks...)\n"
"  --L1 alias1               Sisendfaili 1 (baas) näidatava nime asendus.\n"
"  --L2 alias2               Sisendfaili 2 näidatava nime asendus.\n"
"  --L3 alias3               Sisendfaili 3 näidatava nime asendus.\n"
"  -L, --fname alias         Alternatiivne näidatava nime asendus. Tuleb anda "
"kord iga sisendi kohta.\n"
"  --cs string               Tühistab seadistuse. Tuleb anda eraldi iga "
"seadistuse kohta. Näide: --cs \"AutoAdvance=1\"\n"
"  --confighelp              Näitab seadistusi ja nende kehtivaid väärtusi.\n"
"  --config fail             Mõne muu seadistustefaili kasutamine."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The option <option>--cs</option> allows you to adjust a configuration value "
"that is otherwise only adjustable via the configure dialogs. But be aware "
"that when &kdiff3; then terminates the changed value will be stored along "
"with the other settings. With <option>--confighelp</option> you can find out "
"the names of the available items and current values."
msgstr ""
"Võti <option>--cs</option> võimaldab muuta seadistuse väärtust, mida muidu "
"saab muuta ainult seadistustedialoogi vahendusel. Kuid arvesta, et kui "
"&kdiff3; töö lõpetab, salvestatakse muudetud väärtus. Võtmega <option>--"
"confighelp</option> näeb saadaolevate seadistuste nimesid ja nende kehtivaid "
"väärtusi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Via <option>--config</option> you can specify a different config file. When "
"you often use &kdiff3; with completely different setups this allows you to "
"easily switch between them."
msgstr ""
"Võtmega <option>--config</option> saab määrata mõne muu seadistustefaili "
"kasutamise. Kui kasutad sageli &kdiff3; mitme täiesti erineva seadistusega, "
"lubab see võti variantide vahel hõlpsasti lülituda."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignorable command line options"
msgstr "Eiratavad käsurea võtmed"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:289
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Many people want to use &kdiff3; with some version control system. But "
#| "when that version control system calls &kdiff3; using command line "
#| "parameters that &kdiff3; doesn't recognise, then &kdiff3; terminates with "
