msgid ""
"When you selected another file via browsing or finished editing the filename "
"here by pressing &Enter;, the new file will be loaded and compared with the "
"already loaded file(s)."
msgstr ""
"Kui valid sirvides mõne muu faili või lõpetad failinime redigeerimise "
"klahvile Enter vajutades, laaditakse uus fail ja võrreldakse seda juba "
"laaditud faili(de)ga."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:370
